<h1 align="center"> <%= @user.name %>'s Wellness Plan! </h1>
<hr>
<h4 align="center">"To keep the body in good health is a duty... otherwise we shall not be able to keep our mind strong and clear" - Buddha</h4>
<!-- <p>At www.MakeYourLifeBetter.com we beleive in the 3 pillars of well-being, sleep, exercise and nutrion!
   Improve your well-being by tracking your performance in each category!  </p> -->

<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Aggregated Wellness Score - <%= @user.aggregate_score %> / 10 </h1>
</div>

<!-- SLEEP -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Sleep - <%= @user.sleep_score %></h2>
  </div>

  <div class="card-body">
    The ideal amount of sleep is 8 hours a night! <br><br>
    <%= @hours_slept %> hours per night for <%= Time.now.strftime("%B") %>
    <br><br>
    <%= form_tag user_month_sleep_path do%>
    <label>Month:   </label>
    <%= select_month(Date.today) %>
    <%= submit_tag "Daily Overviews" %>
    <% end %>
    <br>
    <%= link_to "Record A Night's Sleep", new_sleep_path %>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<!-- EXERCISE -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Exercise - <%= @user.exercise_score %></h2>
  </div>

<div class="card-body">
    In order to recieve the greatest benifts one should workout at least 4 times a week! <br><br>
    <%= @workouts_average %> per week for the past 4 weeks
  <br> <br>
  <%= form_tag user_month_exercise_path do%>
  <label>Month:   </label>
  <%= select_month(Date.today) %>
  <%= submit_tag "Daily Overviews" %>
  <% end %>
  <br>
  <%= link_to "Record Workout", new_user_exercise_path %>
  </div>
</div>

<br>



<!-- NUTRITION -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Nutrition - <%= @user.nutrition_score %></h2>
  </div>
<div class="card-body">
  The ideal amount of calorie consumption per day is 2500 for males and 2000 for females! <br> <br>
  The ideal distrubution of food types is carbohydrates - 50 %, proteins - 27% and fats - 23%! <br><br>
  <%= @calories %> calories a day for <%= Time.now.strftime("%B") %> <br><br>
  <% @breakdown_hash.each do |key, value| %>
  <%= value %> % - <%= key %>
  <br><br>
  <% end %>

  <%= form_tag user_month_nutrition_path do%>
  <label>Month:   </label>
  <%= select_month(Date.today) %>
  <%= submit_tag "Daily Overviews" %>
  <% end %>
  <br>
  <%= link_to "Record Meal", user_choice_path %>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
